# A Collection of my Ti*k*Z Graphics

As a fan of [PGF/Ti*k*Z](http://sourceforge.net/projects/pgf/), I made a number of Ti*k*Z Graphics when I wrote my PhD Thesis and some other teaching documents at Sheffield University. This project includes all of these graphics. 

*See the project homepage, [Ti*k*Z Gallery](http://khaos.github.com/TikZGallery/), for more information.*
